@startuml
!theme plain
title 运行时按需授权 · 端到端时序

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor         #1976D2
  ActorBorderColor   #1976D2
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  ParticipantBorderColor #1976D2
}

actor "用户" as U
participant "Options / SidePanel\n(React UI)" as UI
participant "openai-compat\nengine.isAvailable" as ENG
participant "host-permissions\nutil" as UTIL
participant "chrome.permissions\nAPI" as CHROME
participant "第三方 API\n(user's baseUrl)" as API

== 首次使用 · 填配置 ==

U -> UI : 打开 Options\n填 baseUrl / apiKey / model
UI -> UI : openaiCompatConfig.set()
UI -> UTIL : hasHostPermission(originPattern)
UTIL -> CHROME : permissions.contains\n({origins: [...]})
CHROME --> UTIL : false
UTIL --> UI : false
UI -> U : 显示『需要授权此域名』按钮

== 用户点『授权』触发 request ==

U -> UI : 点『授权 api.deepseek.com』
UI -> UTIL : requestHostPermission(originPattern)
UTIL -> CHROME : permissions.request\n({origins: [...]})
CHROME -> U : 弹权限窗\n『允许 / 拒绝』
U --> CHROME : 允许
CHROME --> UTIL : true
UTIL --> UI : true
UI -> U : ✅ 授权成功\n『可以翻译了』

== 翻译 · 已授权路径 ==

U -> UI : 点『翻译』
UI -> ENG : engine.run(input)
ENG -> UTIL : hasHostPermission(originPattern)
UTIL --> ENG : true
ENG -> API : POST /v1/chat/completions
API --> ENG : 200 { choices: [...] }
ENG --> UI : "机器学习是..."
UI --> U : 展示译文

== 翻译 · 用户在 Chrome 设置里撤销权限 ==

U -> CHROME : chrome://extensions\n关掉此站点权限
CHROME -> UTIL : onRemoved 事件
UTIL -> UI : notify permissions changed
UI -> UI : 刷新 isAvailable 缓存

U -> UI : 再次点『翻译』
UI -> ENG : engine.run(input)
ENG -> UTIL : hasHostPermission
UTIL --> ENG : false
ENG --> UI : throw PermissionRequiredError\n{ origin, pattern }
UI -> U : 展示『权限已被撤销，重新授权』CTA\n(可再走 request 流程)

@enduml
